@hitler_chancellor
on-arrival: chancellor = "Hitler"; chancellor_party = "NSDAP"

There is no path to a majority government for now. The scheming around King George V is leading to only one path - that of Chancellor Adolf Hitler. [? if largest_party == "NSDAP" : Since they are the largest party, it is not exactly contrary to parliamentary procedure, so it is difficult to raise objections solely on procedural grounds. ?] [? if hitler_deported: Despite his earlier deportation, the Nazi leaders and their reactionary allies have connived for the king to give him German citizenship after all. ?]

- @hitler_takes_power: What now?

# if NSDAP is largest party and George V is king, then George V appoints Hitler chancellor.

@ccf_majority
